      • createProcessContext

        public static de.uni.freiburg.iig.telematik.sewol.context.constraint.ConstraintContext createProcessContext(java.lang.String name,
                                                                                                            java.util.Collection<AbstractTransition<?,?>> transitions)
        Creates a new context on basis of the given Petri net transitions.
        Transitions are converted into a list of activity names.
        参数:
        name -
        transitions - Petri net transitions to be used as basis for activity names.
        返回:
        抛出:
        de.invation.code.toval.validate.ParameterException - If activity list is null or empty.

      • createRandomContext

        public static de.uni.freiburg.iig.telematik.sewol.context.constraint.ConstraintContext createRandomContext(java.util.Collection<AbstractTransition<?,?>> transitions,
                                                                                                           int originatorCount,
                                                                                                           java.util.List<java.lang.String> roles)
        Creates a new context using an RBAC access control model.
        Users and permissions to execute transactions are randomly assigned to the given roles.
        Each person is assigned to exactly one role.
        参数:
        transitions - A collection of Petri net transitions.
        originatorCount - The number of desired originators.
        roles - The roles to use.
        返回:
        A new randomly generated Context.
        抛出:
        de.invation.code.toval.validate.ParameterException
